        <h4>
          You don't have to spend all your time thinking about what you're
          doing, you just let it happen. No worries. No cares. Just float and
          wait for the wind to blow you around. When you buy that first tube of
          paint it gives you an artist license.
        </h4>
        <p>
          Any little thing can be your friend if you let it be. Think about a
          cloud. Just float around and be there. Isn't that fantastic that you
          can create an almighty tree that fast? You want your tree to have some
          character. Make it special. Just go out and talk to a tree. Make
          friends with it. Have fun with it.
        </p>

        <p>
          Let's put some happy trees and bushes back in here. We touch the
          canvas, the canvas takes what it wants. Automatically, all of these
          beautiful, beautiful things will happen. Just take out whatever you
          don't want. It'll change your entire perspective. There it is.
        </p>

        <p>
          That's what makes life fun. That you can make these decisions. That
          you can create the world that you want. We don't need any guidelines
          or formats. All we need to do is just let it flow right out of us.
          Imagination is the key to painting.
        </p>
